        "body": "<p>There is nothing in documentation about such case and from what I know Navigation Drawer is usually used from sides.<\/p>\n\n<p>You may however check gravity<\/p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/reference/android/support/v4/widget/DrawerLayout.html#openDrawer%28int%29\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://developer.android.com/reference/android/support/v4/widget/DrawerLayout.html#openDrawer%28int%29<\/a><\/p>\n\n<p>There are also other navigation components like Bottom navigation which may fit better in your case.<\/p>\n",
